Application of the FCPortugal Setplay Framework to the Helios Simulation
2D team (http://en.sourceforge.jp/projects/rctools/ , mainly in japanese).

This package depends on the FCPortugal Setplay package, freely available on
http://sourceforge.net/projects/fcportugalsetplays/

To build this package, please follow these steps:
- ./configure --with-setplaydir=DIR (where DIR is where you downloaded the 
FCPortugal Setplay package to)
- make

The executables will be created inside the 'src' directory. To run setplays,
please create the necessaru setplay.conf file and place it in the 'src' 
directory.

Please check the documents with 'agent2d' on their filenames to see relevant 
info on the Helios team.

